    <h1>About YOGOTOCHINA</h1>
    
    <p><strong>I grew up in China and lived there for many years. For the past two decades, I've been based in the Netherlands, but I return to China every year to travel.</strong></p>
    
    <p>With years of experience in the travel industry, I know both sides: the China I grew up in, and the questions European travelers have. Every recommendation on this site comes from personal experience, not from a brochure.</p>
    
    <p>This site is for travelers who want to see China beyond the clichés. The real China. Not always easy to find, but always worth it.</p>
    
    <p>YOGOTOCHINA is independently run. No government affiliation. No travel agency. Just honest, practical, and up-to-date information from someone who knows the country inside out.</p>
